``export def``
[link: /commands/categories/core.md] ’Ł@9028d61a19d4cae413fcaa0ce3b4c45b6e963e5e1ca10fe98b7b2015efed6520ŁgTitle: title: export def
Path: Signature
Content:
``> export def {flags} (def_name) (params) (block)``
’Ł@d273b18ab6fb36cac0c2733e5c63a64571630e77e5d62a0a1518ce97bfdc5e40ŁĒTitle: title: export def
Path: Flags
Content:
``--env``
: Environment: defined inside the command.
``--wrapped``
: Unknown flags and arguments: strings that require rest-like parameter in signature.
’Ł@f16c67bd6a5f3624502ddc6e1d5721b87aba39219d031fbfc4e349dcb20405f6ŁŲTitle: title: export def
Path: Parameters
Content:
``def_name``
: Command name to define.
``params``
: Command parameters: comma-separated list inside 
[
]
.
``block``
: Command body: list of instructions inside {}.
