’Ł@ad49cbc14ecdea375e966958766b6ba06261b8720f0b681767b91ed9fa4ac542ŁĘTitle: title: export def
Path: Examples
Content:
Define a custom command in a module and call it.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> module spam { export def foo [] { "foo" } }; use spam foo; foo
foo

```
